&nbsp;
The Israeli offensive on <a href="https://www.agi.it/estero/news/2024-05-16/Israeli-announcing-nuove-truppe-rafah-26416471/">Rafah</a> continues: according to Hamas, the Israeli army has made new attacks that have caused the death of two people in the Berber refugee camp. And while the Idf reported the bodies of three Islamic hostages - Shani Louk, Amit Buskila and Itzhak Gelerenter> - "brutally murdered" during the escape from the music festival Nova on October 7, the army announced it was engaged in "floating" in Jabalia, in the northern part of the Gaza Strip.
